[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+      190[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mThe problem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m The diagram shows [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mPatient Portal / EHR -->|New Message Event| EventBridge -->|Route| Lambda[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;192;197;206m. EventBridge invokes the Lambda; the Lambda does not call EventBridge. So the Lambda's VPC does not need an EventBridge endpoint for this flow, which is fine. But a reader unfamiliar with EventBridge-to-Lambda invocation might assume they need the endpoint. A half-sentence of clarification is cheap.[K
