[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 146     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mSuggested fix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Clarify: "VPC interface endpoints (PrivateLink) for Bedrock ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcom.amazonaws.{region}.bedrock-runtime[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;192;197;206m), CloudWatch Logs, and KMS. Gateway endpoints for S3 and DynamoDB. Interface endpoints require security groups allowing HTTPS (443) inbound from the Lambda subnet."[K
