[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 241     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe opening problem statement ("Patients love it. Staff hate it.") immediately establishes stakes and is backed by real burnout data. The 47-message inbox scenario is viscerally relatable to anyone who has worked in healthcare IT.[K
[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 242     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The explicit framing of LLMs as "drafting assistants, not autonomous agents" is the correct safety posture and is stated clearly and repeatedly. This is the single most important design decision in the recipe and it's well-defended.[K
[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 243     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The Technology section teaches LLM concepts (hallucination, temperature, constrained generation) without any vendor names. A reader on GCP or Azure learns just as much. The 70/30 balance is well-maintained.[K
[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 244     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The intent classification insight in "The Honest Take" (classification matters more than model choice) reflects genuine deployment experience and is non-obvious to readers who haven't built this.[K
[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 245     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The approval rate as north star metric is the right operational framing. The recipe gives concrete thresholds (70%+ good, below 50% investigate) that are actionable.[K
[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 246     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Provider-specific tone tuning (Dr. Martinez says "Take care," Dr. Patel says "Best regards") is a small detail that demonstrates real-world understanding of what makes these systems succeed or fail.[K
[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 247     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The sample output JSON is complete and shows all the metadata a reader would need to understand the data model.[K
[0m[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 248     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The "resist the temptation to expand scope" warning in the Honest Take is exactly the right advice and is delivered with appropriate conviction.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+      316[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe 5:30 PM inbox opening is the best recipe opener in the book so far. Specific, human, immediately relatable. Keep it.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+      317[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The LLM failure-mode section is a reusable teaching unit. Hallucination, tone drift, over-helpfulness, prompt injection, context window, inconsistency. Concrete examples, not abstract warnings. Other chapters should reference this section rather than restate it.[K
